        <mxCell id="NnAtaQwtMPyeiySuS-tP-1" parent="1" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;overflow=hidden;rounded=0;" value="&lt;h1 style=&quot;margin-top: 0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;MCP Use Cases/Scenarios&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;h1 style=&quot;margin-top: 0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255)); font-weight: normal;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;1. Agent to call an external API - Tool&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;2. Agent to call a utility or function (Ex: Python function) - &lt;b&gt;Tool&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;3. Agent wants to get a knowledge context. Ex: Files&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;.4. Agent to call a database&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255)); font-weight: normal;&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;5. Agent to communicate with an MCP&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: medium; background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;6. Agent to call a prompt template&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;7. Agent call a prompt (especially useful for A/B testing due to versioning capability if it is externalized)&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;Extended scenarios&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;1. Agent calling Agent&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;2. Tool providers (Composio)&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;Other Capabilities:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;1. Caching - Response, session, token&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;2.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;Agent may needs reusable tool orchestration to expose a single capability/workflows/Response aggregation&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;3. Auth and Policy enforcement&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;Dev and Maintenance&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;1. Control pane/monitoring pane&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;2. Configuration option to create MCP server&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;3. Domain/Team isolocation&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" vertex="1">
